SUMMARY:Chocolate and Wine Pairing
DESCRIPTION:Wine & Chocolate Pairing Experience in Davis \nSaturday\, April 18 | 12–5pm\nIndulge your senses with a decadent afternoon of wine and chocolate at its finest. Join us at Great Bear Vineyards for a tasting experience that celebrates the irresistible harmony between our handcrafted wines and silky Lindt chocolates. \nEach pairing is thoughtfully curated to highlight the interplay of flavor\, texture\, and aroma—from bright bubbles to rich\, velvety reds and luscious dessert wines. Take your time\, savor each bite and sip\, and discover just how magical this pairing can be.\n Suggested Pairings:\n– White Chocolate (Gold Wrapper) → Sparkling Brut (Méthode Champenoise)Crisp bubbles meet creamy sweetness for an elegant finish\n– Caramel Chocolate (Dark Gold Wrapper) → MalbecLayers of cherry\, blackberry\, spice\, and caramel richness\n– Pistachio Chocolate (Green Wrapper) → White Port-Style Dessert WineNutty\, aromatic\, and beautifully honeyed\n– Dark Chocolate 70% (Black & Gold Wrapper) → Ruby Port-Style Dessert WineDeep\, intense\, and perfectly balanced\n Prefer to keep it sparkling? You’re welcome to enjoy two flutes of our Sparkling Brut in place of the pairings.\nUnwrap\, sip\, and treat yourself to a little moment of indulgence in the vineyard. Because some pairings are simply meant to be.
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/chocolate-and-wine-pairing-3/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Wine-glasses_web-54l55t.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
